              <string>Reflex (GFF: Ref). BYTE 0–255. Engine reads via ReadFieldBYTE in
               LoadPlaceable. Reflex save value for the placeable; used in some save checks.
               Modders: often 0 in vanilla; set higher for placeables that should resist
               reflex-based effects (e.g. area spells).</string>
             </property>
             <property name="sizePolicy">
